headline.print_headline: Oshie Latest Success Story From Tiny Minn. Town
headline.main: Oshie Latest Success Story From Tiny Minn. Town

lead_paragraph: As T.J. Oshie was leading the U.S. men's team to a dramatic 3-2 shootout win over Russia in Sochi on Saturday, his tiny Minnesota hometown was celebrating the Olympic success of yet another of its hockey players and wondering if he'd be the latest to medal.
